#

Herb-Crusted Grilled Chicken Breast with Garlic Mashed Cauliflower and Roasted Asparagus

$15.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-CarbHigh-Protein

Tags:

ChickenLow-CarbHealthyGourmet

Description

A succulent herb-crusted chicken paired with creamy garlic mashed cauliflower and perfectly roasted asparagus for a satisfying and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Fresh thyme: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Cauliflower: 1 head, chopped into florets
  • Unsalted butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Heavy cream: 1/4 cup
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
